Presenting the official trailer of 'Kis Kisko Pyaar Karoon 2', starring Kapil Sharma, Manjot Singh, Hira Warina, Tridha Choudhary, Parul Gulati and others. This is a sequel to the blockbuster 'Kis Kisko Pyaar Karoon', Kapil Sharma's debut film.  #KisKiskoPyaarKaroon2 #KapilSharma #ManjotSingh

snippet.title: [URDU] 2025 PMGC League | Group Green Day 1 | PUBG MOBILE Global Championship
snippet.description:
Khush aam deed PUBG MOBILE GLOBAL CHAMPIONSHIP 2025 k stage "Group Stage" mai! Paish e Khidmat hai Group GREEN ka pehla din.
Jahan afsaanay bune jaate hain, aur har drop, har rotation, aur har clutch moment ka apni wuqat bayan krta hai!

Grand Finals tak ka safar har match ke saath aur mushkil hota jae ga, to apni kursi ki peti baandh lijiye, snacks haath mein lijiye, aur tayyar ho jaiye ek aur din k world class PUBG MOBILE action k liye! 🏆🔥

Is saal ka format dobara badla gaya hai taa k shaiqeen aur waqar k peche bhagny wali teamain dono ko zyada lutf haasil ho.
Pehla bara twist "The Gauntlet Stage" hai, 
Duniya ki 16 behtareen teamain yahan bary dao laga kr muqabla karen gi.
Dao Pech? Har mumkin lagaye jayen gy.

Rank 1 ta 7: Seedha Grand Finals mein pohanch jayen gi.
Rank 8 ta 16: Group Stage se ek aur mauqa hasil ho ga.

Group Stage mai har group se upper ki 3 teamain seedha Grand Finals ke liye qualify kr jayen gi.
Jo teamain 4th–11th par thin unko Last Chance khelny ka akhri mauqa mile ga.
Lekin jo 12th–16th par aayegi, unka 2025 PMGC ka safar yahin khatam ho jayega.
Aakhir mein, Last Chance (Dec 6 ta 7) teamon k liye aakhri parao hoga.

Yahan do din, or do mawaqy hongy.
Top 2 spots hasil karen, ya shaiqeen k sath beth kr Grand Finals ka nazara dekhen.

Khush aamdeed, 2025 PUBG MOBILE GLOBAL CHAMPIONSHIP Mai — Jahan sarbulandi hasil krny k liye ek Faisla Kun Jung Hogi!

Abhi PUBG MOBILE khelen:  https://pubgmobile.go.link/25pmgc
💰Kul Inaami Raqam : Eight hundred forty seven million PKR - 3,000,000$

🗓️ Group Stage:

snippet.description:
#Netflix #StrangerThings #StrangerThings5

🎥 Attention viewers! (ITS FAN MADE)
Experience the beginning of the end with this Stranger Things Season 5 VOLUME 2 Trailer, bringing a final look at the epic conclusion to Netflix’s biggest series. Featuring fan-favorite characters like Eleven (Millie Bobby Brown), Mike Wheeler (Finn Wolfhard), Will Byers (Noah Schnapp), Lucas (Caleb McLaughlin), Max (Sadie Sink), Dustin (Gaten Matarazzo), Robin (Maya Hawke), Steve Harrington (Joe Keery), Nancy (Natalia Dyer), Jonathan (Charlie Heaton), Joyce Byers (Winona Ryder), and Chief Hopper (David Harbour), the final season sets the stage for a showdown with Vecna (Jamie Campbell Bower). This concept trailer captures the tone of the Stranger Things Season 5 Official Teaser, Final Season Trailer 2, and all the emotional stakes fans have been waiting for as Netflix’s iconic story reaches its climactic end.

The inspiration behind this video:
The long-awaited Stranger Things Season 5 VOLUME 2 Trailer has arrived, giving fans their deepest look yet at the final chapter of Netflix’s biggest phenomenon. As the Stranger Things Season 5 story pushes toward its epic conclusion, the new footage expands on what we saw in the Stranger Things 5 Final Season Trailer 2 and the Stranger Things 5 Official Teaser, delivering darker stakes, emotional reunions, and the return of the Upside Down’s deadliest threat, Vecna. With anticipation at an all-time high, viewers around the world are searching for every detail connected to the Stranger Things Final Trailer and the final showdown ahead.

The cast—Millie Bobby Brown, Finn Wolfhard, Noah Schnapp, Caleb McLaughlin, Sadie Sink, Gaten Matarazzo, Maya Hawke, Joe Keery, Natalia Dyer, Charlie Heaton, Cara Buono, Winona Ryder, and David Harbour—returns for their biggest fight yet, alongside Jamie Campbell Bower as Vecna. Fan-favorite characters like Chief Hopper, Eleven, Mike Wheeler, Dustin, Lucas, Max, Jonathan Byers, Joyce Byers, Will Byers, and Steve Harrington take center stage as the Hawkins crew prepares for war. Netflix is setting the stage for a massive finale, supported by global excitement around the Stranger Things Trailer, St5 Trailer, and every new look released.

Trailer communities such as Rotten Tomatoes TV, Teaser PRO, FilmSpot Trailer, MovieGasm, KinoCheck, EmergencyAwesome, and IGN TV Trailer, along with countless TV Promos, continue to break down every frame. With growing interest in Stranger Things Season 5 Volume 2, the Stranger Things Season 5 Volume 2 Trailer, Stranger Things Season 5 Part 2, the Stranger Things Season 5 Part 2 Trailer, and the evolving narrative teased in the Stranger Things 5 Trailer Volume 2, fans are preparing for a finale that promises to be unforgettable. This is the final battle for Hawkins—and the world is watching.

snippet.description:

Watch the 'FAN (CONCEPT) Trailer Concept' For Stranger Things - Season 5 (2025) (More Info About This Video Down Below!)

▶️ Watch More Concept Trailers:

Get ready for the epic conclusion of Netflix's beloved sci-fi horror series with the Stranger Things Season 5 trailer. Set to premiere in November 2025, this final season promises to deliver a thrilling culmination to the Hawkins saga. After delays caused by industry strikes, production wrapped in December 2024, and post-production is ahead of schedule . The Duffer Brothers have crafted an ambitious season described as "eight blockbuster movies," focusing on emotional depth and high-stakes action .

The narrative centers on the Hawkins crew's ultimate battle against Vecna, delving deeper into the mysteries of the Upside Down. Expect a return to the series' roots with a blend of early dynamics and significant character development, particularly highlighting Will's coming-of-age journey . The season will also explore the eerie, time-frozen nature of the Upside Down, potentially incorporating a time jump to align with the aging cast .

The main cast returns, including Millie Bobby Brown, Finn Wolfhard, David Harbour, Winona Ryder, Gaten Matarazzo, Caleb McLaughlin, Noah Schnapp, Sadie Sink, Natalia Dyer, Charlie Heaton, Joe Keery, Maya Hawke, Priah Ferguson, Brett Gelman, Cara Buono, and Jamie Campbell Bower . New additions like Linda Hamilton and Amybeth McNulty join the ensemble, adding fresh dynamics to the story. The eight confirmed episode titles, including "The Crawl," "The Vanishing of…," and "The Rightside Up," hint at a season filled with intrigue and adventure . Don't miss this climactic and nostalgic conclusion to the iconic series.

Topic: Ayam e Fatima 2025 - Shahadat Bibi Fatima
Mesum Abbas releases his latest Bibi Fatima Noha for Ayyam e Fatima 2025 titled “Ya Zahra” after Ya Fatima.

The noha “Ya Zahra (sa)” is a unique and historic collaboration between Syed Mesum Abbas, a renowned Urdu nohakhwan, and Mulla Hussain Faisal, a respected Iraqi radood based in Bahrain.

For the first time, an Urdu kalam has been recited fully in an Iraqi andaaz, bringing together two powerful traditions of aza:

Urdu language × Iraqi style of recitation

Recorded entirely in Bahrain/USA, this kalam carries the depth of Iraqi recitation and the emotional power of Urdu poetry, combining them into one heartfelt expression of the grief of Bibi Fatima-tuz-Zahra (sa).

This noha reflects a simple truth:
Azadari is not limited to one culture, one people, or one style — it unites all lovers of Bibi Zahra (as).
